cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC

The paper focuses on the energy consumption and optimization of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for image and video applications, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of GPUs for acceleration also suggests a possible connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the study involves multi-GPU servers, which could relate to distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC).
